---
title: Baked Beef & Gnocchi Ragu With Roasted Peppers
description: We love good Baked Beef & Gnocchi Ragu With Peppers and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-beef-gnocchi-ragu-56a9042e-0c61a04f.jpg
